{"tid":318972,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[魔獸世界]60年代萬人私服召喚老屎忽or新人加入","createTime":"2017-07-12T12:54:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-20T13:08:56.000Z","uid":74309,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fdd28ebb43abcfa7894c3d34ca7b3103391325d6","tid":318972,"uid":74309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T12:54:48.000Z","msg":"首先個server係N服前身  因為法律問題之前被暴雪告 搞到執柒左 <br />\n然後而家成個server搬左去俄羅斯境內再開 <br />\n今次暴雪唔會再搞得到架啦  <br />\n所以大家可以放心玩 所有資料都有保留  唔洗驚一夜之間乜都冇<br />\n而家想招大量香港人一齊加入一邊吹水一邊玩 <br />\n希望夠人開到個屬於香港人既公會<br />\n RC:26900268 (絕不小圈子)<br />\n同時亦召喚返以前一齊玩過既巴絲打回歸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所有設定同當年官服一模一樣 係難升架啦 如果玩開速食game既你請上一頁</span></span><br />\n官網開AC: <a href=\"https://elysium-project.org/play\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Felysium-project.org%2Fplay&d=BQoWquJAM8OzImBuufav%2FE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=5f1fc6dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://elysium-project.org/play</a><br />\nDL完game之後係game file到搵返&quot;realmist&quot;呢個文件檔出黎 然後將入面既野改做set realmlist <a href=\"http://logon.elysium-project.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flogon.elysium-project.org&d=BQoWquJAM8OzImBuufav%2FE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=b9f1f17c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">logon.elysium-project.org</a>  (讀取server既路徑)<br />\nsever name : Elysium<br />\n今年一月尾先開服 所以而家加入唔會太遲 有心一定追得到  <br />\n有任何問題歡迎上RC搵我一齊吹水一齊玩  幫到一定幫 答到一定答 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2c5a22cee03faaf478bf412ce2da5eca5fa89b7","tid":318972,"uid":74309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T12:57:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"062f9eeaa7058ae78461c9f684cf5010a52fe8fc","tid":318972,"uid":74309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T13:00:02.000Z","msg":"<img s